Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.28,0:00:04.04,Style2,,0,0,0,,Toto dílo je fiktivní.\NPostavy, místa a organizace jsou smyšlené.\NProsíme dodržujte dopravní předpisy \Na jezděte opatrně.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.88,0:00:09.55,Style2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Get it all right, don't wonder why{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.55,0:00:13.51,Style2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even though trouble's on the way{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.42,0:00:48.59,Style2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Live for yourself{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.59,0:00:51.86,Style2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You can do what you want{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.86,0:00:54.83,Style2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't give up on your dreams{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.83,0:00:58.10,Style2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Better make a start{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.10,0:01:01.74,Style2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Open up your eyes{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.74,0:01:04.61,Style2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You will find your own way{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.61,0:01:07.44,Style2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't want to miss the sign{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.44,0:01:11.01,Style2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Life is like a trick or treat{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.01,0:01:15.05,Style2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Doesn't matter what people may say{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.05,0:01:17.42,Style2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What they say{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.42,0:01:20.46,Style2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No more live in chains{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.46,0:01:23.46,Style2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hold your thoughts and you'll be fine{\i0}
