Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.81,0:01:42.74,Style2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even though trouble's on the way{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.74,0:01:45.31,Style2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now or never, make it better{\i0}
